048        private void handleCommentAfterQName(Token matchedToken) {
049            final char c;
050            try {
051                c = input_stream.readChar();
052            } catch (IOException e) {
053                return;
054            }
055            if(c == ':') {
056                final int len = image.length();
057                for(int i = 0; i < len; i++) {
058                    switch(image.charAt(i)) {
059                        case '(':
060                            input_stream.backup(len - i + 1);
061                            image.setLength(i);
062                            matchedToken.kind = QName;
063                            matchedToken.image = image.toString();
064                            SwitchTo(OPERATOR);
065                            return;
066                        default:
067                            break;
068                    }
069                }
070            } else {
071                input_stream.backup(1);
072            }
073        }
